# Cloudflare Pages / Netlify redirects.
#
# Expose the machine-readable accuracy feed under a friendly URL so partners
# can hit https://oraclebull.com/accuracy.json directly instead of the raw
# edge-function URL.
#
# NOTE: must be 302 (redirect), NOT 200 (proxy). Cloudflare Pages rejects a
# 200 proxy to an EXTERNAL absolute URL ("Proxy (200) redirects can only point
# to relative paths"), which broke the deploy. 302 bounces the client to the
# Supabase function instead of proxying it, and works on both Cloudflare and
# Netlify.
/accuracy.json    https://qynszkirmcrldqmiplwh.supabase.co/functions/v1/accuracy-feed   302